* Develop two versions of Asteroids using Javascript. One of them using CSS, the other one using Canvas.
* Deadline will be Sep 29, 2011. All thursday we'll meet on #jsve in freenode at 22.00h VE to discuss individual progress and solve issues.
* Previous wednesday must be defined the schedule of topics for the meeting in the mailing list [4]
* Every meeting has a DIFFERENT secretary
* You can't use ANY library. Pure Javascript

